data.description: Perfect home for a first time home buyer or ideal investment property. The home features a spacious master suite with a full bathtub on opposite end of home where two additional bedrooms are located. Making this ideal for a family or roommates. Located close to Santa Fe and Evans it's perfect for getting to I-25 and just a short drive to downtown or mountains to get the most of Colorado living!
